videos.description: Zion Williamson comes up with a steal and flushes a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Zion explodes for two-handed jam

videos.description: Virginia's Jay Huff rises up for a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Huf hammers dunk down low

videos.description: Braxton Key skips a pass to Kihei Clark who nails the 3-point shot.
videos.headline: Clark's corner 3 steals momentum

videos.description: RJ Barrett pushes the pace and sets up Cam Reddish for an open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Reddish hits transition 3-ball

videos.description: Tre Jones throws ahead to RJ Barrett who flushes a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Barrett leaks out for wide-open dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson shows off his athleticism as he hustles back to a wide-open Virginia player and flies for a nasty block.
videos.headline: Zion elevates for vicious block

videos.description: Cam Reddish dishes to Zion Williamson, who finishes with an arena-silencing dunk.
videos.headline: Reddish sets up Zion for dunk

videos.description: RJ Barrett says he was playing with the "mamba mentality" in No. 2 Duke's win vs. No. 3 Virginia.
videos.headline: Barrett played with 'mamba mentality' in win vs. Virginia

videos.description: RJ Barrett, Zion Williamson and Cam Reddish combine for 61 points as No. 2 Duke beats No. 3 Virginia 81-71.
